title: Ep 380 | The Birthplace of 'Duck Dynasty' & When Jase Beat All His High School Coaches at Dominoes
description:
Jase reveals the secret to Miss Kay’s sweet potato pie. Jase shares the made-up history of the Robertson clan. Al and Jase relive the family's legendary arguments at the card and domino table. Jase remembers the day he beat every one of his high school coaches at dominoes. And Phil reveals where they got the idea for "Duck Dynasty."
